N:copilot-coding-agent
D:GitHub Copilot Coding Agent automation. Add the ai-copilot label to an issue → GitHub Actions assigns Copilot via GraphQL → Copilot auto-creates branch+code+Draft PR. One-click issue-to-PR pipeline.
G:copilot github-actions issue-to-pr draft-pr graphql automation ai-agent
U[5]:
  Start Copilot auto-implementation with issue + label only
  Offload backlog (refactors/docs/tests) to Copilot
  Delegate follow-up work from Vibe Kanban/Conductor to Copilot
  External systems (Jira) → GitHub Issue → Copilot PR pipeline
  Team focuses on PR review; Copilot handles implementation
S[4]{n,action,details}:
  1,Setup,bash scripts/copilot-setup-workflow.sh (one-time)
  2,CreateIssue,gh issue create --label ai-copilot --title "..." --body "..."
  3,OrLabel,gh issue edit <num> --add-label ai-copilot (existing issue)
  4,Check,gh pr list --search 'head:copilot/' && gh pr view <num>
R[4]:
  Copilot Pro+/Business/Enterprise plan required
  First PR requires manual approval from someone with write access (treated as an external contributor)
  PAT needs repo scope (COPILOT_ASSIGN_TOKEN secret)
  More detailed issue descriptions improve Copilot output quality
E[3]{desc,in,out}:
  "Setup","bash scripts/copilot-setup-workflow.sh","Auto-configure secret+workflow+label"
  "Issue→PR","gh issue create --label ai-copilot --title 'Add auth' --body '...'","Copilot creates branch+writes code+opens Draft PR"
  "Manual assign","bash scripts/copilot-assign-issue.sh 42","Assign Copilot to issue #42 immediately"
